DESCRIPTION:	Caution: This email originated from outside of the organizat
 ion. Do not click links or open attachments unless you recognize the sen
 der and know the content is safe. \n\n\nDear all\,\n\n \n\nWe are lookin
 g forward to the welcome event\, in preparation for your participation o
 n the EMEA Next Generation CFO Academy.\n\n \n\nDuring this welcome even
 t\, we will provide an introduction to your Academy journey\, meet the t
 eam and your peer group. The session will run 9:00-11:00 CEST.\n\n \n\nI
 t is an important session so please make every effort to attend.\n\nThis
  session will run virtually prior to the in-person event which commences
  on Monday 18 May 2026\, in Paris.\n\n \n\nMore details will be provided
  in due course.\n\n \n\nThank you and we look forward to seeing you in t
 he session!\n\n \n\nEMEA CFO Programme Team\n\n \n\nThis message (includ
 ing any attachments) contains confidential information intended for a sp
 ecific individual and purpose\, and is protected by law. If you are not 
